      "source": [
        "## 2. Target or proxy\n",
        "\n",
        "*What would you predict? Where does that label come from — observed outcome or a defined rule?*"
      ],
      "id": "qRenYiMHBAnx"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "What I am predicting: Whether a page will see a positive turnaround or growth trend post-refresh.\n",
        "\n",
        "Where the label comes from: This will be a defined rule (proxy label) built from observed historical outcomes in the data. We will define a successful target candidate using a rule such as: trend_direction == 'up' combined with a filter ensuring the page has an organic baseline (impressions_90d > 100)."
